---
// お問い合わせページ
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  
  <title>お問い合わせ | 三原市まち歩き - PHOTO MAP</title>
  <meta name="description" content="三原市まち歩き - PHOTO MAPへのお問い合わせはこちらから。">

  <script is:inline src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zen+Maru+Gothic:wght@500;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
  
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Zen Maru Gothic', sans-serif; 
      color: #1a1a1a; 
      background-color: #f8f9fa; 
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .serif-custom { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; }
    
    /* ▼ 完全切り替え用のCSS ▼ */
    .lang-jp, .lang-en { display: none; }
    body.is-jp .lang-jp { display: block; }
    body.is-jp span.lang-jp, body.is-jp a.lang-jp { display: inline; }
    body.is-en .lang-en { display: block; }
    body.is-en span.lang-en, body.is-en a.lang-en { display: inline; }
  </style>

  <!-- ▼ 言語判定プログラム ▼ -->
  <script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
        let lang = urlParams.get('lang');
        
        if (!lang) {
             lang = localStorage.getItem('siteLang') || 'jp';
        }
        
        if (lang === 'en') {
            document.body.classList.add('is-en');
            document.title = "Contact | Mihara Walk - PHOTO MAP";
            const backLink = document.getElementById('back-link');
            if(backLink) backLink.href = '/?lang=en';
        } else {
            document.body.classList.add('is-jp');
            const backLink = document.getElementById('back-link');
            if(backLink) backLink.href = '/?lang=jp';
        }
    });
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  
  <nav class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 sticky top-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-between shadow-sm">
      <a href="/" id="back-link" class="text-[#004098] font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm flex items-center gap-2 hover:opacity-70 transition">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> 
        <span class="lang-jp">トップページへ戻る</span>
        <span class="lang-en">Back to Top</span>
      </a>
      <div class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 tracking-widest uppercase">Mihara Rediscover</div>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white min-h-screen shadow-sm mt-6 mb-12 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    
    <div class="px-6 sm:px-12 py-10 sm:py-16 text-center">
       
       <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#004098] serif-custom mb-8 tracking-wide">
           <span class="lang-jp">お問い合わせ</span>
           <span class="lang-en font-sans">Contact Us</span>
       </h1>

       <div class="lang-jp text-left mb-10">
         <p>当サイトに関するご質問、写真掲載の取り下げ依頼、その他のお問い合わせにつきましては、以下の専用フォームよりご連絡ください。<br>
         内容を確認次第、運営者よりご連絡させていただきます。</p>
       </div>
       <div class="lang-en text-left mb-10">
         <p>For questions regarding this site, requests to take down posted photos, and other inquiries, please contact us using the dedicated form below.<br>
         The administrator will contact you after confirming the contents.</p>
       </div>

       <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdQps3FxrrZlenFlyMxRZG1URw0yOb4QJYJCsiNbPTnRFonUA/viewform?usp=publish-editor" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-[#004098] text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors shadow-md">
           <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> 
           <div class="text-left">
             <span class="lang-jp">お問い合わせフォームを開く</span>
             <span class="lang-en">Open Inquiry Form</span>
           </div>
       </a>
       
       <div class="mt-16 text-left bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
           <h3 class="font-bold text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2 flex items-center">
             <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info text-blue-500 mr-2"></i>
             <span class="lang-jp">写真の掲載に関するお問い合わせ</span>
             <span class="lang-en">Inquiries Regarding Photo Posting</span>
           </h3>
           <div class="lang-jp text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
             <p>もし、ご自身が権利を持つ被写体（人物・私有地など）が意図せず掲載されており、削除をご希望の場合は、該当ページのURLを添えてフォームよりご連絡ください。速やかに対応いたします。</p>
           </div>
           <div class="lang-en text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
             <p>If a subject (person, private property, etc.) to which you hold the rights has been posted unintentionally and you wish to have it deleted, please contact us via the form with the URL of the relevant page. We will respond promptly.</p>
           </div>
       </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="text-center bg-white border-t border-gray-200 padding py-10 mt-auto">
    <p class="text-[9px] font-bold text-gray-400 tracking-widest uppercase">© 2026 Mihara Walk Photo Map</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>